-   <span data-ttu-id="b0338-408">en-GB.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0338-408">en-GB.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b0338-409">Angielski (Wielka Brytania)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b0338-409">English (United Kingdom)</span></span>  
  
